This directory is a vendored copy of the Rust server source from:

    SpacetimeDB monorepo, demo/Blackholio/server-rust
    commit 353557cede4dd8cab1dd0a31f93677e175609bda (tag v2.6.0-26-g353557ced)

Local changes to the upstream source (Apache-2.0 section 4(b)):

  1. Cargo.toml — dependency pinned to spacetimedb = "2.5.0", so the module
     builds against the SpacetimeDB CLI version this SDK is tested with.
  2. src/lib.rs — added `probe_vector3` / `probe_error` / `probe_params` procedures and their
     `Vector3` type,
     used only by the SDK's wire-fixture tests. Marked in-file. No upstream
     code was altered or removed.
  3. src/lib.rs — added the `probe_row` table, its `ProbeKind` enum and the
     `probe_seed` reducer, carrying the column shapes stock Blackholio has none
     of (Option fields, a sum/enum column, u128/u256/i128 columns). Used only by
     the SDK's wire-fixture tests. Marked in-file. No upstream code was altered
     or removed.

See README.md for rationale.
